The paper proposes a new framework for managing and mining geo-tagged multimedia data, which involves database management, multimedia processing, information retrieval, deep learning, and computer vision. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.DB (Databases), followed by cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.DL (Machine Learning), and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
